>\n<br />\n而家建制派俾到盡先得41席<br />\n點夠2/3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而你自爆辭多幾件就唔夠都變夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盧思達今次柒撚左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係計全體70席<br />\n唔係剩餘幾席</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我喺另一個post見人話剩餘，真係唔知點計</blockquote><br />\n好似政改呢種既就計全體70席<br />\n但踢議員走既就在席既2/3<br />\n如果d多兩個，即係41席就過2/3"},{"pid":"453eb2bf94a606237bffb76441113eb6ec0ffe12","tid":325560,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泛民這一刻已失1/3否決權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全體立法會議員2/3先可以過議案<br />\n70席計即係建制最少要47<br />\ndq左6件 64席計即係最少要43席<br />\n<br />\n而家建制派俾到盡先得41席<br />\n點夠2/3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而你自爆辭多幾件就唔夠都變夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盧思達今次柒撚左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係計全體70席<br />\n唔係剩餘幾席</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我喺另一個post見人話剩餘，真係唔知點計</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/procedur/content/partk.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Fprocedur%2Fcontent%2Fpartk.htm&d=O%2FRWeA2pu0Ji7bc9PnC4oL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=cfdaeb48\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/procedur/content/partk.htm</a><br />\n如贊成&quot;行政長官按照《基本法》第四十九條發回的......(法案名稱)經重議後予以通過&quot;的議案的議員數目不少於<span style=\"color: red;\">全體議員三分之二多數</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/invest/invest_1216.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Finvest%2Finvest_1216.htm&d=O%2FRWeA2pu0Ji7bc9PnC4oL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=da105898\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/invest/invest_1216.htm</a><br />\n根據《基本法》第七十九(七)條，立法會議員如有行為不檢或違反誓言而經<span style=\"color: red;\">立法會出席會議的議員三分之二</span>通過譴責，<br />\n而家知鄭松泰點解同泛民咁「合作」未<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}